	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td width="10%" nowrap="nowrap">Post subject:&nbsp;</td>
		<td><b>Re: Idea for cell-shaded FMV on the NES</b></td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />True so long as you know you can encode any positive length, not topping out at 127 or 255 or whatever. For this, I'd recommend either a Golomb code or an Exp-Golomb code (such as the gamma code).

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


	<hr width="85%" />

